Privacy Policy for Add It Up!

Introduction

Welcome to Add It Up! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application. By using Add It Up!, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect

Add It Up! does not directly collect any personal information from users. However, the application incorporates third-party services that may collect information as described below:

Admob

We use Admob, a third-party advertising service, to display advertisements in Add It Up!. Admob may collect certain data to provide personalized advertisements and improve its services. This data may include:

Device information: such as device type, operating system, and device identifiers.

Usage data: including app interactions and viewed ads.

For more details on the data collected by Admob, please review their Privacy Policy.

How Information Is Used

The information collected by Admob is used to:

Display relevant advertisements.

Analyze app performance and user interaction to improve the overall experience.

We do not have access to or control over the data collected by Admob.

Third-Party Advertisements

Admob provides:

Banner Ads: Displayed at the bottom or top of the app interface.

Interstitial Ads: Full-screen ads that appear at natural transition points.

Rewarded Ads: Optional video ads that provide in-game rewards upon completion.

These advertisements are managed by Admob and may include personalized content based on user preferences.

Data Sharing

Add It Up! does not share any personal information with third parties. However, data collected by Admob is managed according to their policies and may be shared with their partners as outlined in their Privacy Policy.

Children’s Privacy

Add It Up! is not directed at children under the age of 13. If you believe your child has provided information through our app, please contact us, and we will take steps to remove such information.

Data Security

We are committed to ensuring the security of your information. While we do not collect or store personal data, we work with trusted third-party services that implement appropriate security measures.

User Rights

As a user, you have rights regarding your data, including:

Opting out of personalized advertisements via your device settings.

Reviewing and managing data collected by Admob.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the “Last Updated” date will reflect the most recent revision.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:

Email: [plgameschile@gmail.com]

